  "baseRefName": "main",
  "body": "## Summary\n\n- **scripts/checks/**: 14 check scripts يغطون كامل دورة الحياة — file manifest، schema contracts، business OS catalog، need intelligence، account pack، email quality gate، proposal gate، delivery gate، client acceptance، security/privacy، agent governance، deliverability، launch scorecard، scale readiness\n- **cli.py**: 4 أوامر جديدة — `launch-score`، `scale-score`، `founder-command [--dry-run]`، `war-room [--dry-run]`\n- **docs/success/**: DEALIX_SUCCESS_ARCHITECTURE_AR.md + MARKET_SELECTION_AR.md (باقي الـ 53 ملف قيد الإنشاء بواسطة content agent)\n\n## Architecture overview\n\n```\n5 War Rooms:\n├── Founder War Room     → reports/founder/\n├── Revenue War Room     → reports/account_intelligence/ + outreach/ + proposals/\n├── Delivery War Room    → reports/delivery/\n├── Agent Governance     → docs/agents/ + reports/agents/\n└── Scale War Room       → reports/scale/ + deliverability/\n\n4 Scores:\n├── Launch Score         (reports/launch/LAUNCH_SCORECARD.md)\n├── Scale Score          (reports/scale/ULTIMATE_SCALE_SCORECARD.md)\n├── Delivery Health      (reports/delivery/DELIVERY_HEALTH_SCORECARD.md)\n└── Agent Governance     (reports/agents/AGENT_PERMISSION_AUDIT.md)\n```\n\n## Test plan\n- [ ] `python -m py_compile scripts/checks/*.py` — جميع السكريبتات صالحة نحوياً\n- [ ] `python scripts/checks/check_file_manifest.py` — يعمل ويطبع PASS/FAIL\n- [ ] `python cli.py war-room --dry-run` — يطبع هيكل الـ 5 غرف\n- [ ] `python cli.py founder-command --dry-run` — يطبع قالب DAILY_SUPER_COMMAND\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01RfN1x6mWiRurss9TwwAgtD\n\n---\n_Generated by [Claude Code](https://claude.ai/code/session_01RfN1x6mWiRurss9TwwAgtD)_",
