      "messageBody": "Docs (AR-primary, bilingual):\n- docs/acquisition/: CALL_BRIEF_SYSTEM_AR\n- docs/business_need_intelligence/: SPECIALIZED_SPRINT_LIBRARY_50_AR (50 sprints)\n- docs/delivery/: pipeline, acceptance, sign-off, weekly value reports\n- docs/finance/: margin model, cash priority score\n- docs/followup/: FOLLOW_UP_CADENCE_AR\n- docs/operating_factory/: daily loop, weekly loop, role ownership\n- docs/outreach/: SYSTEM_BASED_OUTREACH_PLAYBOOK_AR\n- docs/privacy/: do-not-contact policy, client data handling\n- docs/proposals/: MINI_PROPOSAL_FACTORY_AR\n- docs/scale/: delivery capacity planning\n- docs/security/: prompt injection defense, untrusted input sandboxing\n\nReport templates (5 war rooms):\n- reports/founder/: daily super command, war room daily/weekly, execution control board\n- reports/account_intelligence/: TOP_100_ACCOUNT_QUEUE\n- reports/outreach/, acquisition/, proposals/, finance/\n- reports/delivery/: pipeline, blockers, sign-off queue, health scorecard, value report queue\n- reports/agents/: daily activity review, permission audit\n- reports/security/: audit log, daily security review\n- reports/scale/: ultimate scorecard, weekly review, sector expansion, capacity review\n- reports/deliverability/: domain health, daily review\n- reports/launch/: LAUNCH_SCORECARD (35-item weighted checklist)\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01RfN1x6mWiRurss9TwwAgtD",
